; Script by HuKuTa94
; use this script in ai/start field for default pack (stock) TGC characters 

; !!! WARNING !!!
; use this script on 1-layer level only

; vars description and manual: you can change editable vars to setup character as BOSS or DEFAULT

; editable vars:
; isBoss		// 0 - for default zombies; 1 - for boss zombie (spawned in boss wave only)


;===============================================================

;// var declaration
:state=0:dimlocalvar=isBoss

;======= EDITABLE VARS =========
:state=0:setvar=isBoss 0
;===========================


;===============================================================

;// run setup script from Shoot field
:state=0:floorlogic,alwaysactive=0,shootplr
